{"tid":1464523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我想知道機場集會嘅目的係咩","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:53.000Z","uid":197005,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c23d7e37c8b6046cce42e2ff53439a76fe79f39f","tid":1464523,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"一邊話係要阻止旅客上機<br />\n一邊話只係向旅客和平宣傳<br />\n<br />\n其實我地目的係要令所以外國人唔好再嚟香港<br />\n因為佢哋一但嚟 就會消費 從而刺激經濟<br />\n刺激經濟=對成個局面冇幫助<br />\n<br />\n最重要係貨運嚟唔到香港=損害緊香港經濟<br />\n<br />\n但依家變咗一批人要塞死departure<br />\n一批人反對塞departure 只係安靜坐喺度宣傳<br />\n跟住兩邊互屌<br />\n<br />\n港支共唔係我地最大嘅敵人<br />\n分化先係<br />\n<br />\n所以行動之前<br />\n唔該先傾掂數<br />\n塞旅客又好 齋坐安靜宣傳都好<br />\n點都唔好割席<br />\n但大家需要有一致方向<br />\n咁先容易行動 從而成功"},{"pid":"4a4a5eb37f5dc85f5002daea48198159fea948e0","tid":1464523,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］大家唔好再嘈啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e6d9c73db106be65ed12237bfa599d5668aa4b0","tid":1464523,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"btw 818遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735341ae3082fbc234cb0a24d7e252d343922647","tid":1464523,"uid":75702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb808cb25b6c91ab021807e9619695d66edabfe2","tid":1464523,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"我想要討論唔係一堆宣傳第二個post..."},{"pid":"5bdb492cf370db32c0ecfe49da40e589793d0274","tid":1464523,"uid":123898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"各有各做 但請勿分化"},{"pid":"9c797e0835e0942e9093c493a8fce0f723314f57","tid":1464523,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bdb492cf370db32c0ecfe49da40e589793d0